THIS SOFTWARE IS DEPRECATED AND HAS NO CURRENT SUCCESSOR. UPDATES ARE NOT PROVIDED.

Step 1:
Extract the folder into your HTTP serving directory.

Step 2:
Make sure PHP, MySQL, php5-curl and Postfix are installed.

Step 3:
Edit includes/db_connect.php and change the MySQL host, user (if applicable) and password. Note: This is only for creating users and initially setting up the system. The user must have user creation and modification privileges.

Step 4:
Run setup.php

Step 5:
Go to index.php and create an account.

Step 6:
Please send patches, update apps, add apps, etc, to da.ndart@googlemail.com

